tion) into\\\\n                             InternalSpec. Deterministic prompt template, no LLM.\\\\n      - jobs_db.py           SQLite job state at /home/user/cypherclaw-data/\\\\n                             image_jobs.db. WAL mode, thread-safe per-call conns.\\\\n                             Lifecycle: queued → running → uploading → terminal.\\\\n      - gemini_backend.py    google-genai wrapper with model override support;\\\\n                             default gemini-3-pro-image-preview (Nano Banana Pro);\\\\n                             lazy SDK import so tests inject fakes cleanly.\\\\n      - s3_uploader.py       boto3 wrapper, scoped to PutObject on jobs/* prefix;\\\\n                             returns direct S3 HTTPS URL.\\\\n      - worker.py            sync core process_job_sync + async schedule_job;\\\\n                             WorkerHooks injection seam for tests.\\\\n      - app.py               FastAPI factory create_app(s, db, hooks) — no module\\\\n                             singleton so importing the package never touches the\\\\n                             filesystem (clean test ergonomics).\\\\n      - __main__.py          uvicorn entry: `python -m cypherclaw.image_api`\\\\n      - config.py            env-var Settings dataclass with from_env classmethod\\\\n    \\\\n    Systemd unit: my-claw/systemd/cypherclaw-image-api.service\\\\n      - User=user, EnvironmentFile=/home/user/cypherclaw/.env (AWS keys)\\\\n      - Restart=always with backoff; hardened (NoNewPrivileges, ProtectSystem,\\\\n        ReadWritePaths=/home/user/cypherclaw-data only)\\\\n      - Default port 9000, host 0.0.0.0 (tailnet-bound only at deploy)\\\\n    \\\\n    Tests (51 new, all passing locally; 3264 total still green):\\\\n      - test_image_api_spec_parser   Shape A + B + project-slug coherence + errors\\\\n      - test_image_api_jobs_db       insert/get/update lifecycle, list_pending,\\\\n                                     persistence across reopen, pare